---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Us | AI Native Digital Agency"
  description="Learn about our AI-native digital agency and how we help companies in their product engineering journeys."
>
  <Header />
  
  <main>
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <section class="pt-32 pb-12 md:pt-40 md:pb-20 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
            About Us
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
            We're an AI-native digital agency helping companies transform their businesses through innovative product engineering.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Our Story -->
    <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
            Our Story
          </h2>
          <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
            <p>
              Founded in 2018, AI Agency was born from a simple yet powerful idea: to help businesses harness the transformative power of artificial intelligence in their product engineering journeys.
            </p>
            <p>
              Our founders, a team of experienced engineers and product strategists, recognized that while AI was rapidly evolving, many companies struggled to effectively implement these technologies in ways that created real business value.
            </p>
            <p>
              We set out to bridge this gap by building a team of experts who not only understood the technical aspects of AI and product engineering but also had the business acumen to align technology solutions with strategic objectives.
            </p>
            <p>
              Today, we're proud to work with innovative companies across various industries, helping them leverage AI-native approaches to transform their products, services, and operations.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Our Mission -->
    <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
            Our Mission
          </h2>
          <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
            <p>
              Our mission is to empower businesses to thrive in the AI era by providing expert guidance and implementation of cutting-edge technologies that drive meaningful results.
            </p>
            <p>
              We believe that successful digital transformation isn't just about implementing new technologiesâ€”it's about reimagining how businesses operate, engage with customers, and deliver value in a rapidly evolving digital landscape.
            </p>
            <p>
              Through our collaborative approach, we work closely with our clients to understand their unique challenges and opportunities, developing tailored solutions that leverage AI and other emerging technologies to achieve their strategic goals.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Our Values -->
    <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-10">
            Our Values
          </h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-12">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
                Innovation
              </h3>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
                We constantly explore new technologies and approaches to solve complex problems and create exceptional digital experiences.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
                Collaboration
              </h3>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
                We believe the best solutions emerge from close collaboration with our clients, working together as partners rather than just service providers.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
                Excellence
              </h3>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
                We're committed to delivering the highest quality work in everything we do, from strategy and design to development and implementation.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
                Integrity
              </h3>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
                We operate with transparency and honesty, building trust through ethical practices and responsible use of technology.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
                Impact
              </h3>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
                We measure our success by the tangible business outcomes we help our clients achieve, focusing on solutions that drive real value.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Team -->
    <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
            Our Team
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
            Meet the experts behind our AI-native solutions.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Team Member 1 -->
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md">
            <div class="h-64 bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-700 relative">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 w-16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">
                Sarah Johnson
              </h3>
              <p class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mb-4">
                CEO & Co-Founder
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">
                With over 15 years of experience in technology leadership, Sarah drives our strategic vision and ensures we deliver exceptional value to our clients.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Team Member 2 -->
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md">
            <div class="h-64 bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-700 relative">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 w-16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">
                Michael Chen
              </h3>
              <p class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mb-4">
                CTO & Co-Founder
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">
                A pioneer in AI and machine learning, Michael leads our technical team and ensures we stay at the cutting edge of emerging technologies.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Team Member 3 -->
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md">
            <div class="h-64 bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-700 relative">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 w-16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">
                Emily Rodriguez
              </h3>
              <p class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mb-4">
                Head of Product Strategy
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">
                With a background in both design and business, Emily helps our clients translate their vision into successful digital products.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
